Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:59.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,Fusion of cat and gecko, Catgecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,For Operation: F to succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:50.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,you must first lure out Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:55.60,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(677.167,370.389)}Eerie \NThe Bloodthirsty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:55.60,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Black Cat Paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Big Brother still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But when night falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you came\Nto ask for our help, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, he's acting really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come by and stand watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:22.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,The black cat paintings, painted\Nwith the blood of devils...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:28.41,Italics,,0,0,0,,You can use your self-replicating\Ncells to travel freely between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.88,Italics,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Monster!\N- My name is Catgecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo will have heard of the\Nlocked-room murders by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Catgecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is your next target!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, why don't you tell\NMr. Hongo the whole story again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru's big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His big brother, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was acting weird,\Nthen suddenly he collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was mixing his blood in with paint to\Npaint all these weird black cat pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops. Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen him in three\Ndays, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. A minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I can tell this to,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but Taki's on orders from the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From the FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at four o'clock at Nishiatami Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to hold a peace conference with\Nfamous scientists from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So Taki's running security...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no exaggeration to say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that world peace lies in the\Nhands of the scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If Gel Shocker attacks them,\Nawful things could result.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now for the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An investigation on the mysterious serial murders\Nthat occurred last night has hit a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:20.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The lead investigator, who will hold a\Npress conference at three o'clock today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gel Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Catgecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Catgecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one behind\Nthe locked room murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We mean to kill our enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, and the entire Rider Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Catgecko can travel through\Nthose paintings at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:51.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,He was mixing his blood in with paint to\Npaint all these weird black cat pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working for Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to Catgecko's hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is right before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Catgecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... we'll\Nfinish this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:44.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the next time we\Nmeet, I will kill you all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,by slipping through a black cat painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:57.00,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the security layout for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\c&H000000&\3c&H2269A5&}Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seemed awfully plain in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any time bombs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to execute Operation: F.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, our plan to kidnap\Nthe world's greatest scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Catgecko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to me, General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now attack the\NRider Corps headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider, Hongo Takeshi,\Nis sure to appear then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in accordance with\Nyour orders, General Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will travel to the\Nconference room's painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider travels fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will still take him twenty minutes\Nto reach a location eighty kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you'll be\Nable to kidnap the scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that Japan...\Nno, all of Asia can be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Kamen Rider Kid Corps headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, phone call from Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone send you a painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The black cat in that painting is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster will leap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no black cat in the painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine... just stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about, a black cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Mr. Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no black cat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Corps... I'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have your way while I am here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Pops, take Yuri and the others to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope, with confidence,\Nit'll be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black, preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be combat-ready at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All preparations are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Catgecko... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe our inventions are best\Nwhen used in the interests of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace conference Taki\Nis doing security for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be in progress as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they wanted to draw me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Nishiatami Hotel is\N80 kilometers from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Catgecko can travel between cat paintings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,even if they're a hundred kilometers away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's Hongo! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is Hongo. Listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,Is there a picture of a\Nblack cat in that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,You have to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,The black cat works for Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please remain calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! A Gel Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always getting stronger, Catgecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the scientists!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:18.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:26.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:34.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:41.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:07.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:14.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:22.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:30.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:52.92,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Swimming through the\Noceans with a Rider Swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:22:00.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great dive flitting through the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:04.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up whirlpools with a Rider Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:08.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dragging enemies down with a Rider Lung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:11.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! I have another weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My Gecko Sucker Feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... I will suck\Nout all of your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fearsome plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the boys' friend's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It should cheer Satoru up\Nto see him back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:01.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's ambitions were\Nfoiled by Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker wouldn't\Nbe easily dissuaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:05.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in the name of justice and peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:10.72,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:14.05,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:12.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first phase of Operation: Pet involves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:20.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,using Canarycobra's venom to\Nmake the people of Tokyo go mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Geldam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:24.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fill the Earth with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, let's meet again for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:31.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"The Terrifying Operation:\NPet - Send Rider to Hell!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:31.05,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs105\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Terrifying Operation: Pet\N Send Rider to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:58.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:02.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:06.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:09.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:13.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eerie - The Bloodthirsty\NBlack Cat Paintings!